(** relation: lower_algorithm2
 **
 ** Helper relation to lower_algorithm
 ** inputs:  (Exp.Exp list /* inputs   */,
              Exp.Exp list /* outputs  */,
              int          /* numnodes */, 
              int          /* aindx    */)
 ** outputs:  (Equation list) 
